* Iron Raptor had stopped when Prowl had motioned her to do so, she looked past him and saw a damaged bot stumble into the clearing ahead.
She recognized that bot despite the damages and gashes on his body, it was Zenyak! She knew him, he was the first bot she had ever met on this planet.
Iron Raptor growled under her breath and dug her hind claw into the soft soil of the under growth, she just happened to hate him a little more then the rest!
She watched silently as Prowl had climbed into a near by tree and then had launched himself into the air, he had hit Zenyak fairly hard in the back of the shoulders and had knocked him unconscious.
As Prowl had transformed into robot mode Iron Raptor entered into the clearing and looked down at the bot at Prowl's feet.*

" Excitant!"

* She lowered her snout level with Zenyak's face to get a closer look at him  but then pulled her head back up to her full height and looked at Prowl, he had pulled off that attack perfectly.*

" Impressive as well."

* Iron Raptor looked around at the surrounding forest and sighed, they had caught themselves a bot. Now what?
She looked back at Prowl and smiled, but she was proud of him to say the least.*

" What do we do with him now?"
